==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Shot-free
<hw>Shot"-free`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not to be injured
by shot; shot-proof.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Feltham.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shot-free</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Shot-free
<hw>Shot"-free`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Free from charge or expense;
hence, unpunished; scot-free.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shotgun</ent>⟦br⟧
